Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Billy Martin leaves Yankees
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bt6d
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Jul 1978
NY Yankees manager Billy Martin quits. Lesson in where the buck stops in the Western world. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less